<p>is also my of my chief weaknesses at present &amp; in the company of my pal spend many an hour at the good old game.  Frank Grose left YM on Wednesday 3.4.18 for London &amp; from there will proceed to France.  Met Bill Phillips &amp; Tom Martin a week or so back rather a pleasant meeting, since then Bill Phillips has proceeded overseas.  Have been before a few medical boards during the period &amp; am now classified B2.A. which means 6 month service in England. At times get</p>
